            . I am a constable in my own right. I received the prisoner with this handkerchief.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was returning from my brother's to Eyre-street-hill, where I live - I was running, and the watchman told me to stop, which I did; a young man brought the handkerchief from the top of the street, and I was at the bottom.</p>
